data.text: @reel_villan My Wife, Sister and Dad have all had their first doses - same vaccine. My Sister and Dad have weakened immune systems also (Wife works in care). They all felt a little groggy next day and sore arm, but nothing more. Paracetamol and Ibuprofen, plenty of water.
@reel_villan 😂😂😂 Was looking forward to an extra limb disappointed tbh
@corbo184 Bonus! Haha. I don't think I would even realise the difference as I have been sleeping a lot with my chemo and everything. I'll probably notice if I grow a third arm or something though...
@reel_villan Was best sleep I had for ages 😂
@corbo184 Good stuff and glad you got your first one too. Hopefully this is a step in the right direction for us!
@reel_villan Only thing I've had is tiredness and slight ache where jab was taken bud. Happy to hear you had your first dosage
